msg: [CXF-100] Partial fix: Support configuration of interceptors at service and endpoint level (bus was already done in previous commit), even when these are created by the runtime (as opposed to IOC container). See ConfiguredEndpointTest in rt-frontend-jaxws and associated configured-endpoints.xml for an example.
Add boolean property "validating" and getters to EndpointImpl - use to determine if schema validation should take place.
